[section#syntax
    [:en] Syntax notation
	[:zh_CN] 语法表示法
]

[index:begin@text#syntax
	[:en] syntax
	[:zh_CN] 语法
]


[para]
[:en]
In the syntax notation used in this International Standard, syntactic categories
are indicated by [em@gram italic] type, and literal words and characters in
[em@code constant] [em@code wide] type.
[:zh_CN]
在本国际标准所使用的语法表示法中，语法范畴用[em@gram 楷体字]表示，字面词汇和字符
用[em@code 等宽字体]表示。

[:en]
Alternatives are listed on separate lines except in a few cases where a long set
of alternatives is marked by the phrase ["[=OneOf].]
[:zh_CN]
候选条目分别列在各自的行中，少数情况下一长串候选条目用短语“[=OneOf]”标明。

[:en]
If the text of an alternative is too long to fit on a line, the text is
continued on subsequent lines indented from the first one.
[:zh_CN]
如果某候选条目太长而不能以一行列出，则其文本将在后续行中列出，并相对于第一行
进行缩进。

[:en]
An optional terminal or non-terminal symbol is indicated by the subscript
["[=Opt]], so
[:zh_CN]
可选的终结符或非终结符被标以下标“[=Opt]”，于是

[syntax:sample]
[:en]
[`{] [~:opt expression] [`}]
[:zh_CN]
[`{] [~:opt 表达式] [`}]
[syntax:end]

[~:en]
indicates an optional expression enclosed in braces.
[~:zh_CN]
表示被包围在花括号中的可选的表达式。

[para]
[:en]
Names for syntactic categories have generally been chosen according to the
following rules:
[:zh_CN]
语法范畴的名字通常依据以下规则选择：

[list:ul]

[item]
[:en]
[em@gram X-name] is a use of an identifier in a context that determines its
meaning (e.g., [~class-name], [~typedef-name]).
[:zh_CN]
[em@gram 某名] 是在确定含义的语境中使用的标识符，（如[~类名]、[~typedef-名]）。

[item]
[:en]
[em@gram X-id] is an identifier with no context-dependent meaning (e.g.,
[~qualified-id]).
[:zh_CN]
[em@gram 某标识] 是没有语境相关含义的标识符，（如[~限定标识]）。

[item]
[:en]
[em@gram X-seq] is one or more [em@gram X][=']s without intervening delimiters
(e.g., [~declaration-seq] is a sequence of declarations).
[:zh_CN]
[em@gram 某序列] 是没有分隔符的一个或多个[em@gram 某]，（如[~声明式序列]是一系列
声明式）。

[item]
[:en]
[em@gram X-list] is one or more [em@gram X][=']s separated by intervening commas
(e.g., [~expression-list] is a sequence of expressions separated by commas).
[:zh_CN]
[em@gram 某列表] 是以逗号分隔的一个或多个[em@gram 某]，（如[~表达式列表]是
以逗号分隔的一系列表达式）。

[list:end]

[index:end#syntax]
